  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd -\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Convene Parliament to discuss attack on protesters - main opposition demand",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The opposition United People's Shakti has requested the Prime Minister to convene the Parliament tomorrow, Monday 25th, to discuss the brutal attack on the people who participated in the Khali Mukhatidal People's Uprising.",
        "The chief coordinator of the party and Member of Parliament Laxman Kiriella has made this request through a letter to Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena.",
        "The crackdown and the manner in which the security forces attacked the protestors who were engaged in the peaceful protest at Galle Mukhatidal Kota Ko Kama has had a serious impact on democracy. Many have pointed it out harshly.",
        "Summon Parliament tomorrow, Monday, to discuss the brutal attack on the empty-faced protestors.",
        "Various international community-based organizations and international countries are strongly condemning the heavy attack by the security forces on the empty-faced protestors.",
        "In this situation, this issue will further exacerbate the economic crisis that Sri Lanka is currently facing.",
        "Accordingly, the letter further states that Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardanividam, as the main opposition party, requests that Parliament be convened tomorrow to discuss the attack."
      ],
